# No Full Rebuild (Mandatory ‚Äî Humans and AI)

**Status:** Policy strengthened 2026-07 after CMake Tools configure + vcpkg lock caused 10‚Äì30 minute ‚Äúfull rebuild‚Äù waits on small edits.

## Canonical commands (only these)

| Who | Build | First configure (once per machine) | Recovery |
|-----|-------|-----------------------------------|----------|
| Human | **Ctrl+Shift+B**, `ÎπåÎìú.bat`, `.\scripts\build-release.ps1` | Automatic inside `build-release.ps1` when `build/CMakeCache.txt` is missing | `.\scripts\recover-ide-build.ps1` |
| AI task close | `.\scripts\build-release.ps1` only | Same ‚Äî **never** run `--preset` if `build/` exists | Same recovery script |

**Never** use CMake Tools status-bar **[Configure]** / **[Build]** or F5 with `type: "cmake"`.

## AI agent ‚Äî hard bans

| Do not | Why |
|--------|-----|
| `cmake --preset default` when `build/CMakeCache.txt` exists | Re-runs vcpkg manifest + can block on `vcpkg-running.lock` for 10‚Äì30 min |
| Raw `cmake --build` without `build-release.ps1` | Skips stale-lock recovery; may race CMake Tools |
| Enable `cmake.enabled` or add CMake Tools tasks/launch configs | Hijacks F5 / open ‚Üí configure + vcpkg |
| `cmake --preset` at every task close / version bump | Version bump needs **incremental** `--build` only (~3‚Äì15 s) |
| Parallel `cmake` configure (IDE + terminal + agent) | vcpkg lock deadlock |
| Create `build-clangd/` or second CMake build trees | Wrong IntelliSense + duplicate configure |
| ‚ÄúFix‚Äù slow IDE by re-enabling CMake Tools | Restores the failure mode |

## Expected timings (Release, `build/` present)

| Change | Time |
|--------|------|
| No source changes | ~3 s |
| One `.cpp` | ~5‚Äì15 s |
| `CMakeLists.txt` version bump only | CMake reconfigure + `Application.cpp` + `UpdateChecker.cpp` (~seconds‚Äì1 min) ‚Äî **not** full vcpkg/qtbase rebuild |

If a build takes **>2 minutes** with no new vcpkg dependency, **stop** ‚Äî run `.\scripts\recover-ide-build.ps1`, reload window, use Ctrl+Shift+B only.

## `.vscode/settings.json` invariants

`cmake.enabled: false` plus `configureOnOpen` / `configureOnEdit` / `automaticReconfigure` / `ignoreCMakeListsChanged` / `useCMakePresets: never` / hidden status bar ‚Äî see tracked `.vscode/settings.json`. **Do not** weaken.

